-rules.Action Cards (Initiative)]{Action Card)} of Five or less.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Charge]</td>\n<td>S, V d8, Fighting d8</td>\n<td>At end of run action may make a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Free Attacks]{free attack} with not @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Multi-Actions]{multi-action} penalty.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Close Fighting]</td>\n<td>N, A d8, Fighting d8</td>\n<td>The hero gains a bonus to @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Parry]{Parry} equal to the enemy's weapon @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Reach]{Reach} +1.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Improved Close Fighting]</td>\n<td>N, Close Fighting</td>\n<td>As Close Fighting, but also gaining a +1 bonus to @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Fighting]{Fighting} equal to enemy weapons @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Reach]{Reach} +1.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-edges.Combat Reflexes]{Combat Reflexes}</td>\n<td>S</td>\n<td>+2 @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Spirit} to recover from being @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Damage Effects]{Shaken} or @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Stunned]{Stunned}.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-edges.Counterattack]{Counterattack}</td>\n<td>S, Fighting d8</td>\n<td>Free @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Fighting]{Fighting} attack against one foe per round who failed a&nbsp; roll.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"improved-edge\">@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-edges.Improved Counterattack]{Improved Counterattack}</td>\n<td>V, Counterattack</td>\n<td>As Counterattack, but against three failed attacks per round.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-edges.Dead Shot]{Dead Shot}</td>\n<td>WC, N, Athletics or Shooting d8</td>\n<td>First successful@Compendium[